@page "/about"

<PageTitle>CitySimulator - About</PageTitle>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h2>About CitySimulator 3D</h2>
    <hr />
    <p>
        CitySimulator is a 3D city building simulation developed in C# utilizing Blazor Server and the Three.js library. 
        It simulates a living city with citizens, dynamic weather, daylight cycles, traffic, and economy management.
    </p>

    <h4>Features:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Real-time rendering of a procedurally generated city.</li>
        <li>Automatic management of zones: Residential, Commercial, and Industrial.</li>
        <li>Dynamic day and night cycles affecting lighting.</li>
        <li>Weather effects like rain and fog.</li>
        <li>Simulated economy, population growth, and citizen happiness.</li>
    </ul>

